C407402: Highlight the current scope

Steps
1
Click on menu "All products"
Select first parent category

The category page is opened

2
Click on menu "All products"

The current category scope is highlighted

3
Hover over the category with vc-icon subcategories__arrow
Wait for the second menu to open
Select the subcategory from second menu

The subcategory page is opened

4
Click on menu "All products"
Hover over the category with vc-icon subcategories__arrow
Wait for the second menu to open
Select the subcategory from second menu

The current subcategory scope is highlighted

5
Check all categories from main menu
Repeat steps from 1-4

The current category scope is always highlighted